{
  "stem": "2916.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I quickly covered my whole body and waited and waited and waited, and nobody came into the bedroom.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the conversation is going on in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So against my mother's strict orders, I got out of bed, and I tiptoed to the kitchen door.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the kitchen door was closed, but we had a glass window over it with a curtain that you could see through.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I see my brother talking to my parents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I came into the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was very excited.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was crazy about my older brother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I hugged him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we called him bubbe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's a German nickname, like in English you would say sonny.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because [NON-ENGLISH] is, in Germany, a little boy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so, bubbe is like sonny.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said, bubbe, what are you doing here?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, very quickly, I understood that he came home because he saw-- as he was going to school, he saw German tanks marched into-- march-- marching through the main highway in Budapest, the main boulevard which he had to take a streetcar on in order to go to school.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he must have been a very smart guy, very smart boy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because nobody else did this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were quite a few other young people from Samorin who studied in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody came home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was the only one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Instead of going to school, he turned around, went straight to the train station, took the train home and arrived in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my parents said, why did you come?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and, you know, it cannot be true.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we don't know anything about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, to make a long story short, the next morning my father went to the synagogue, because that was where news reached you.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
